  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to verify efficacy and safety of a bilateral deep brain
      stimulation (DBS) of the Nucleus accumbens (NAc) as a treatment option for severe opioid
      addiction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
